1
00:00:13,939 --> 00:00:14,660
But

2
00:00:16,299 --> 00:00:17,900
why did you help me in the end?

3
00:00:18,939 --> 00:00:20,299
Don't flatter yourself.

4
00:00:21,340 --> 00:00:24,099
If I don't make you the heir,

5
00:00:24,180 --> 00:00:26,419
how can you pay for what you've done?

6
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:30,180
It was your idea to launch a hostile takeover against Su's.

7
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:33,500
It was also your idea to frame us for fraud.

8
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:36,740
If you don't take responsibility, who will?

9
00:00:37,339 --> 00:00:38,740
I've been tolerating you,

10
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,339
being nice to you, and taking care of you,

11
00:00:41,699 --> 00:00:43,619
all to make you fall in love with me.

12
00:00:45,659 --> 00:00:47,420
It's all my plan.

13
00:00:47,939 --> 00:00:49,220
You've never been in love.

14
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:51,339
You don't like people in your circle.

15
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:53,259
You just like white rabbits.

16
00:00:54,059 --> 00:00:55,860
But those white rabbits

17
00:00:55,860 --> 00:00:57,180
were brought by Gu Chengjing.

18
00:00:57,180 --> 00:00:58,420
Why do I take medicine when I'm not sick?

19
00:01:02,859 --> 00:01:04,020
They can't stand you.

20
00:01:05,859 --> 00:01:06,900
You must have done it on purpose.

21
00:01:08,380 --> 00:01:09,540
But I'm different.

22
00:01:10,100 --> 00:01:11,540
I can accept everything.

23
00:01:12,499 --> 00:01:14,419
Because accepting is also part of my plan.

24
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,859
But the dosage isn't enough.

25
00:01:18,619 --> 00:01:19,619
Don't worry.

26
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:21,139
He drinks a lot every day.

27
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:23,300
I put a little bit in each time, so he won't notice.

28
00:01:25,380 --> 00:01:27,139
Aren't you just a dog Gu Chengjing sent

29
00:01:27,139 --> 00:01:28,699
to spy on me?

30
00:01:29,139 --> 00:01:31,499
You've always suspected that I work for Gu Chengjing.

31
00:01:32,540 --> 00:01:34,419
Yes, but not exactly.

32
00:01:34,699 --> 00:01:35,660
You're not sure?

33
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,660
You used to be a gentleman.

34
00:01:44,380 --> 00:01:45,619
But after the accident,

35
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:47,100
you suspect Gu Chengjing

36
00:01:47,259 --> 00:01:48,660
and deliberately lose your temper.

37
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:49,779
Don't you know you can't enter my room

38
00:01:49,779 --> 00:01:50,940
without my permission?

39
00:01:52,259 --> 00:01:53,339
No one told me.

40
00:01:53,339 --> 00:01:54,419
I'm telling you.

41
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,740
Don't enter my room

42
00:01:56,740 --> 00:01:57,619
and touch my things without my permission.

43
00:01:58,419 --> 00:01:59,100
I see.

44
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:00,180
Then get out of here.

45
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:02,259
So I pretend to be pitiful,

46
00:02:02,979 --> 00:02:04,460
you will feel guilty.

47
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:05,580
I'm sorry.

48
00:02:05,619 --> 00:02:06,860
Don't say that.

49
00:02:07,980 --> 00:02:09,420
I shouldn't have said that.

50
00:02:09,619 --> 00:02:11,379
If I treat you very well,

51
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:13,379
you will like me.

52
00:02:24,339 --> 00:02:25,140
I'm hungry.

53
00:02:25,539 --> 00:02:26,499
Get me something to eat.

54
00:02:27,819 --> 00:02:28,539
Of course.

55
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:32,580
[I deliberately let Qi Zhu think I'm marrying into a rich family.]

56
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:34,219
Why are you dressed like this?

57
00:02:34,619 --> 00:02:36,339
Do you really think of yourself as the lady of the house?

58
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:39,539
Don't dress me like this anymore.

59
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,539
You're a woman too.

60
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:48,939
Is this all the tricks you've got?

61
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:52,619
I don't even know how you got married into the Gu family.

62
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,539
Do you really want to marry into the Gu family?

63
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:58,580
[Firstly, to confuse people.]

64
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:00,180
[The most important thing is]

65
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,740
[I deliberately put on a sad play for you to see.]

66
00:03:03,339 --> 00:03:05,020
you'll like me more and more.

67
00:03:07,939 --> 00:03:08,659
Let's go.

68
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,020
What's wrong?

69
00:03:13,379 --> 00:03:15,539
I sprained my ankle

70
00:03:15,659 --> 00:03:17,099
when cleaning the pool.

71
00:03:18,339 --> 00:03:19,339
How do you feel now?

72
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:20,980
Painful.

73
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:28,020
You can ignore it.

74
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:30,180
Mr. Jing also told me to leave him alone.

75
00:03:30,539 --> 00:03:31,420
You all can ignore it,

76
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:32,860
but I can't.

77
00:03:32,939 --> 00:03:33,700
I'm nobody.

78
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:34,939
I'm just a servant.

79
00:03:38,499 --> 00:03:39,460
Help me get ready.

80
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,260
I'll go try on the wedding dress.

81
00:03:49,099 --> 00:03:49,900
You know,

82
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:52,580
I don't want to marry Wanqing.

83
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,460
I want to be with you.

84
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:58,980
After I get the company back on track,

85
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:01,180
I'll come back and marry you.

86
00:04:10,379 --> 00:04:12,099
He slept in the study last night.

87
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,580
He must have fallen for you.

88
00:04:17,859 --> 00:04:18,700
That's right.

89
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:21,739
We are one step closer to our plan.

90
00:04:26,419 --> 00:04:27,380
Let's start the next step.

91
00:04:40,419 --> 00:04:41,219
Give me a bath.

92
00:04:41,620 --> 00:04:42,419
I'll do it.

93
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:46,820
Let Xiaoxue do it.

94
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,339
You go to tidy up first.

95
00:04:48,539 --> 00:04:49,419
Xiaoxue.

96
00:04:51,659 --> 00:04:52,419
Hurry up.

97
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,140
Okay.

98
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:56,580
The acquisition case

99
00:04:56,580 --> 00:04:58,460
is no longer under your control.

100
00:04:58,460 --> 00:04:59,539
The acquisition of the art gallery

101
00:04:59,539 --> 00:05:01,020
is getting more and more attention from the outside world.

102
00:05:01,219 --> 00:05:02,779
If there is no new change,

103
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:04,620
the malicious acquisition

104
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:05,979
will never be removed.

105
00:05:06,219 --> 00:05:06,979
So,

106
00:05:07,659 --> 00:05:09,739
my suggestion is to rebuild the Su's Art Gallery.

107
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:12,460
My suggestion will be reported to the board of directors.

108
00:05:12,859 --> 00:05:15,140
The renovation plan should be followed up immediately.

109
00:05:15,419 --> 00:05:17,979
This will be the biggest help to the company now.

110
00:05:18,179 --> 00:05:19,260
I've been waiting

111
00:05:19,979 --> 00:05:21,979
for the day you can't see anymore.

112
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:56,339
Fortunately, it didn't take long.

113
00:05:56,859 --> 00:05:57,940
You can't see anymore.

114
00:06:00,060 --> 00:06:01,140
I can't see anymore.

115
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:02,700
I'll have to leave the gallery

116
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:04,140
to you.

117
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:06,419
And you'll have to

118
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:08,339
handle some things for me.

119
00:06:10,339 --> 00:06:11,820
Alright, I'll try my best.

120
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:15,179
Ji Xiaoxue, this is your plan?

121
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,179
The data is inaccurate,

122
00:06:17,179 --> 00:06:18,140
and the information is incomplete.

123
00:06:19,859 --> 00:06:21,700
Do you not take my words seriously,

124
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:23,620
or do you not take Mr. Gu's words seriously?

125
00:06:24,179 --> 00:06:25,779
Do you think I did a bad job?

126
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:28,539
That was something I discussed with Wanqing.

127
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,739
It's just an act for the company.

128
00:06:31,659 --> 00:06:33,419
I really didn't do well.

129
00:06:35,299 --> 00:06:36,140
Don't worry.

130
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:37,500
I will collect

131
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,940
all the materials and data.

132
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:40,380
There won't be any mistakes.

133
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:45,260
I was not clear about the details of the acquisition agreement

134
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,500
at that time.

135
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:51,979
That's why you told me the password of your computer.

136
00:06:51,979 --> 00:06:53,260
The password is 35327.

137
00:06:59,659 --> 00:07:01,620
If you don't have the core materials now,

138
00:07:02,539 --> 00:07:03,859
you can't help me.

139
00:07:04,979 --> 00:07:05,900
Then I can find

140
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:08,620
the evidence of your malicious acquisition of Su's Group.

141
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:10,979
Not only did I get the evidence,

142
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,900
but I also want your Gu family

143
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:15,539
to personally revive the Su's Art Gallery.

144
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,779
After all this is done,

145
00:07:20,099 --> 00:07:21,260
it's time for the final step,

146
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,539
which is to put you in the position of heir.

147
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:27,419
I want to give you all the shares

148
00:07:27,419 --> 00:07:28,179
Mr. Gu gave me.

149
00:07:28,779 --> 00:07:29,500
No.

150
00:07:29,979 --> 00:07:30,779
I can't take it.

151
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,700
I only trust you.

152
00:07:34,179 --> 00:07:36,299
I won't give them to Gu Chengjing.

153
00:07:39,299 --> 00:07:40,979
Don't let us down,

154
00:07:42,099 --> 00:07:42,739
okay?

155
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:47,460
I can't attend your wedding.

156
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:49,820
I'm not going to invite you.

157
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,099
Because I've discussed with the board

158
00:07:52,739 --> 00:07:54,539
to kick you out of the Gu family.

159
00:07:56,739 --> 00:07:58,179
Now Gu Chengjing has been

160
00:07:58,179 --> 00:07:59,219
driven out of the Gu family.

161
00:08:02,979 --> 00:08:03,659
You

162
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:06,219
have tasted the feeling of being a father

163
00:08:06,219 --> 00:08:07,299
you've also felt it.

164
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:10,460
And you,

165
00:08:10,859 --> 00:08:11,820
Gu Chengyan,

166
00:08:12,659 --> 00:08:16,179
you should pay the price for your selfishness.

167
00:08:17,859 --> 00:08:20,179
Don't you want to continue your father's

168
00:08:20,179 --> 00:08:20,979
business?

169
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,460
Now you can't.

170
00:08:32,059 --> 00:08:33,459
I believe this evidence

171
00:08:34,699 --> 00:08:36,220
will give us justice.

172
00:08:44,620 --> 00:08:46,419
Wanqing, let's go.
